column5: 1st Dec PM-Christmas fair to save a school swimming pool
column6: The school is hosting a Christmas Fayre to raise money to refurbish their swimming pool that is used by the children in the local community. Volunteers needed to set up, run and pack up the stalls. Can make it a fun day with your family.
